    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it's looking for a great new home. This car has been super reliable for me and is still in wonderful shape\u2014perfect for daily commutes or weekend adventures! It\u2019s been well-loved and runs really smoothly, so you\u2019re getting a fantastic deal on a solid vehicle. I've taken great care of it, and I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to come see it in person or take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of the legendary S54B32 platform. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six delivers linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline, managed by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, rod bearing replacement, and proactive rear subframe reinforcement. The chassis retains its signature 50/50 weight distribution, further sharpened by upgraded bushings and a refreshed cooling system. While the aesthetic condition reflects its status as a well-loved driver\u2019s car, the drivetrain performance remains uncompromisingly sharp. Ready for spirited use or continued preservation.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Well-maintained vehicle. Reliable engine. Clean interior. Minor exterior wear. Full service history. Runs well.",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a remarkably well-kept vehicle that perfectly bridges the gap between luxury and daily reliability. The exterior retains a brilliant luster, showing only the minor, expected signs of careful road use. Inside, you'll find a pristine, smoke-free cabin with supple leather seating and a dashboard free of sun damage or cracks. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, operates flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine runs quiet and strong, backed by a comprehensive service history and a recently completed multi-point inspection. This car has been loved and it shows\u2014it\u2019s ready to provide its next owner with years of dependable, stylish transportation.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, offering a refined driving experience and proven reliability. This unit has undergone a comprehensive professional inspection to ensure its mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal meet our rigorous standards. Boasting a consistent service history, it represents an exceptional value for the discerning driver who prioritizes both performance and longevity. Experience the perfect intersection of quality and investment value.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my trusty ride and it's looking for a great new home. It\u2019s been super reliable for me and is still in really wonderful shape, inside and out! It drives like a dream and has been well-loved, with just the usual minor character you'd expect from a car that's actually been enjoyed. If you're looking for a solid, stylish car that won't let you down, this is the one. Come by and take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 31500.0,
