      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of the high-revving S54 platform. The 3.2L inline-six features individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system that pulls cleanly to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and sent to the rear wheels through a functional M-Variable limited-slip differential. Essential preventative maintenance has been addressed, including subframe reinforcement and a VANOS bulletproofing, ensuring the chassis handles high-G cornering without compromise. The suspension retains its factory-spec MacPherson strut and multi-link geometry, offering the precise feedback and neutral balance the chassis is known for. While displaying minor cosmetic patina typical of a well-enjoyed driver, the powertrain and drivetrain remain tight and responsive.",
      "price": 34500.0,
